{"tid":2433252,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[轉載]  正告立場新聞：你有你編輯自主 人家都有批評的言論自由","createTime":"2021-03-04T23:25:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-05T00:47:51.000Z","uid":141151,"like":23,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7ce1bd0ce0199a0c6402f755bcc2a31145d594fd","tid":2433252,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T23:25:04.000Z","msg":"正告立場新聞：你有你編輯自主 人家都有批評的言論自由<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://jeromyu.medium.com/%E6%AD%A3%E5%91%8A%E7%AB%8B%E5%A0%B4%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E-%E4%BD%A0%E6%9C%89%E4%BD%A0%E7%B7%A8%E8%BC%AF%E8%87%AA%E4%B8%BB-%E4%BA%BA%E5%AE%B6%E9%83%BD%E6%9C%89%E6%89%B9%E8%A9%95%E7%9A%84%E8%A8%80%E8%AB%96%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1-444d9ae39e3b\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjeromyu.medium.com%2F%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E5%2591%258A%25E7%25AB%258B%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E-%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E7%25B7%25A8%25E8%25BC%25AF%25E8%2587%25AA%25E4%25B8%25BB-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E9%2583%25BD%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%2589%25B9%25E8%25A9%2595%25E7%259A%2584%25E8%25A8%2580%25E8%25AB%2596%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25B1-444d9ae39e3b&d=eRHmMhW6fCYgFX7Mu85bUnvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=2ebc897f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://jeromyu.medium.com/%E6%AD%A3%E5%91%8A%E7%AB%8B%E5%A0%B4%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E-%E4%BD%A0%E6%9C%89%E4%BD%A0%E7%B7%A8%E8%BC%AF%E8%87%AA%E4%B8%BB-%E4%BA%BA%E5%AE%B6%E9%83%BD%E6%9C%89%E6%89%B9%E8%A9%95%E7%9A%84%E8%A8%80%E8%AB%96%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1-444d9ae39e3b</a><br />\n<br />\n編按：本來已經寫粵文多時，但明顯要輾壓這些窮酸文人，所以一定要寫這些胡語為「基礎方言」的書面語。<br />\n<br />\n話說週四該行山傳媒的專頁刊出一篇緬甸飲食的文章，文首卻表示「無能為力」，所以介紹食品。一時間很多人指責該媒體食用「人血饅頭」。<br />\n<br />\n然後該網的編輯更加有臉書動態流出，似乎對公審很不滿，更加說媒體是不是要自我審查，可以說是不知悔改。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1*dAu-2-NA9vwg-E3PE77inw.jpeg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmiro.medium.com%2Fmax%2F1400%2F1%2AdAu-2-NA9vwg-E3PE77inw.jpeg&d=eRHmMhW6fCYgFX7Mu85bUnvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=ae655966\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1*dAu-2-NA9vwg-E3PE77inw.jpeg</a><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x6O1qaE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx6O1qaE.jpg&h=b3e920cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">我向來不喜歡這個傳媒，當然不知道這個傳媒是否是很多「社會賢達」的發聲平台，估計是投鼠忌器，我相信大家都不會深究這個媒體。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n但我過往的經驗所得，這個媒體可以說私德不堪，不問自取，或者獲授權一次，就好像永久授權的予取予求的案例屢見不鮮。<br />\n<br />\n所以會再發生這樣人血饅頭事件，實在見怪不怪。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">當然這位編輯絕對有出人血饅頭的言論自由，更可以作出更多在臉書瘋言瘋語。但我以新聞系碩士的學歷正告該等人士，你有這樣的言論自由，自然就要承受網民批評的自由。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/oS9Ey3C_E-U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FoS9Ey3C_E-U&d=eRHmMhW6fCYgFX7Mu85bUnvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=8a53d52a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/oS9Ey3C_E-U</a><br />\n<br />\n我想講清楚的是，如何把關一個專頁，不是自我審查，是傳媒作為公器應盡之責任，也是媒體人的倫理。當然任何人有荒淫無度的自由，或者認為自己給錢自己，自己有權說話，這是商業媒體的本質。但在自由的社會，你就要承受公眾的檢視和批評。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">如果面對公眾的批評，受不了，就用言論自由做擋箭牌，扮無辜又好，企圖壓制言論都好，這樣其實真的和共產黨沒有甚麼分別。</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"d1613dd2eaf87f1cf9e6b273451b9d2d382bdc6d","tid":2433252,"uid":364850,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T23:32:06.000Z","msg":"呢單野真係好過份<br />\n係到消費緬甸<br />\n仲話幫襯間野就幫到人地<br />\n弱智到一個點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a806befe18536fc2fade78c3e511ffd7f654b09f","tid":2433252,"uid":228143,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T23:42:01.000Z","msg":"好似係技稿咩人都寫得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以冇立埸"},{"pid":"e0341298cc987f1fa38bf18d672dd5b46543fffd","tid":2433252,"uid":267410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T00:38:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca1d1af5e9dadb85e1babebdeb8e6a24c28ca7c7","tid":2433252,"uid":57844,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T00:42:56.000Z","msg":"咁睇文匯大公好無！？"},{"pid":"1130e95fe0b2da63431e94fcc258780eafbd0a48","tid":2433252,"uid":7903,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"ca1d1af5e9dadb85e1babebdeb8e6a24c28ca7c7","tid":2433252,"uid":57844,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T00:42:56.000Z","msg":"咁睇文匯大公好無！？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T00:46:06.000Z","msg":"唔係立場就大晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樓主篇野冇屌錯個編輯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係唔睇立場就要睇文匯大公？？？<br />\n你呢種非黑即白嘅二元思維真係要檢討一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e31ce4e611d91c1a4e94cdab02e4782c7bbb276","tid":2433252,"uid":198375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a806befe18536fc2fade78c3e511ffd7f654b09f","tid":2433252,"uid":228143,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T23:42:01.000Z","msg":"好似係技稿咩人都寫得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以冇立埸"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T00:47:41.000Z","msg":"即係好似雞咁任上<br />\n<br />\n呢d 所謂報紙編輯咪就係雞頭 報格就係雞格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f017cd6090efeae1423f841190ef4b929498b59b","tid":2433252,"uid":117301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T00:47:51.000Z","msg":"唔知咁寫係記者意思定食肆要求<br />\n但寫稿記者同間食肆係食人血饅頭<br />\n依個罪名實推唔甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}